Text: Horrible quality for file size. Almost looks like a VHS rip a/v: 5/5. I am downloading another copy so if it was just the actual filming of the movie that was very low quality I apologize, however if you are looking for HD look elsewhere! thanks to to uploader for the effort all the same.
